child, she has never quite found happi-
ness in anyone or anything but her
brother Richie.

Richie, . natural

second
Tenenbaum son, became a tennis star,"
but later suffered a nervousbreakdown
on national television. He went into
exile on a ship somewhere in the
Atlantic, because of — unbeknownst to
anyone —— his love for his adopted sister.

the

Royal Tenenbaum
(Gene Hackman) is the
father of all this dysfunc-
